{"word":"Priest","slug":"priest","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Priest</b> Antemosaic:<br/> - Melchizedek<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=18'>Gen 14:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=6'>Heb 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=11'>Heb 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=20'>Heb 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=7&verse=21'>Heb 7:21</a> <br/> Jethro<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=16'>Exo 2:16</a><br/> - Priests in Israel before the giving of the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=22'>Exo 19:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=24'>Exo 19:24</a> <br/> - Called Angel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=5&verse=6'>Ecc 5:6</a> <br/> Mosaic:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=44'>Exo 29:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=10'>Num 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=7'>Num 18:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=13'>1Ch 23:13</a> <br/> - Hereditary descent of office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=43'>Exo 28:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a> <br/> - Consecration of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=35'>Exo 29:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=16'>Exo 40:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=23'>Lev 6:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=35'>Lev 8:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=7&verse=21'>Heb 7:21</a> <br/> - Is holy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=7'>Lev 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=9'>Lev 22:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=16'>Lev 22:16</a> <br/> - Ablutions of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=32'>Exo 40:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=24'>Lev 16:24</a> <br/> - Must be without blemish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=23'>Lev 21:23</a> <br/> - Vestments of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=43'>Exo 28:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=29'>Exo 39:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=11'>Lev 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=13'>Lev 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=19'>Eze 44:19</a> <br/> - Don vestments in temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=42&verse=14'>Eze 42:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=19'>Eze 44:19</a> <br/> - Atonement for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=6'>Lev 16:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=24'>Lev 16:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=27'>Eze 44:27</a> <br/> - Defilement and purification of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse