://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=42'>Jos 21:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=60'>1Ch 6:60</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=3'>Neh 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=20'>Neh 11:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=6'>Eze 45:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=20'>Eze 48:20</a> <br/> - Own lands sanctified to the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=21'>Lev 27:21</a> <br/> - Tithes of the tithes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=18'>Num 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=32'>Num 18:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=38'>Neh 10:38</a> <br/> - Part of the spoils of war, including captives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=29'>Num 31:29</a> <br/> - First fruits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=20'>Lev 23:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=9'>Lev 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=13'>Num 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=18'>Num 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=5'>Deu 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=36'>Neh 10:36</a> <br/> - Redemption money<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=23'>Lev 27:23</a> <br/> - Redemption money of firstborn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=51'>Num 3:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=16'>Num 18:16</a> <br/> - Things devoted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=21'>Lev 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=10'>Num 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=14'>Num 18:14</a> <br/> - Fines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=16'>Lev 5:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=14'>Lev 22:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=8'>Num 5:8</a> <br/> - Trespass money and other trespass offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=15'>Lev 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=18'>Lev 5:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=9'>Num 18:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=12&verse=16'>2Ki 12:16</a> <br/> - The shewbread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=30'>Exo 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=9'>Lev 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=4'>2Ch 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=11'>2Ch 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=33'>Neh 10:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=4'>Mat 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=2'>Heb 9:2</a> <br/> - Portions of sacrifices and offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=34'>Exo 29:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=3'>Lev 2:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=10'>Lev 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=13'>Lev 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=16'>Lev 5:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=18'>Lev 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=26'>Lev 6:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=10'>Lev 7:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=34'>Lev 7:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=14'>Lev 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=13'>Lev 14:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=20'>Num 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=19'>Num 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=5'>Deu 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=14'>1Sa 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=31'>Eze 44:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=4'>Eze 45:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=13'>1Co 9:13</a> <br/> - Regulations by Hezekiah concerning emoluments (compensations)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=19'>2Ch 31:19</a> <br/> - Portion of land allotted to, in redistribution in Ezekiel's vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=14'>Eze 48:14</a> <br/> - For sustenance of their families<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=13'>Lev 22:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=11'>Num 18:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=19'>Num 18:19</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=6'>Exo 19:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=61&verse=6'>Isa 61:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=9'>1Pe 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=6'>Rev 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=10'>Rev 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=20&verse=6'>Rev 20:6</a><br/> High priest:<br/> - Moses did not denominate Aaron chief or high priest. The function he served was superior to that of other priests. The title appears after the institution of the office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=15'>Lev 21:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=32'>Num 3:32</a> <br/> - For qualifications, consecration, etc.<br/> <a href='S:Priest, Mosaic'>Priest, Mosaic</a> <br/> - Vestments of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=43'>Exo 28:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=31'>Exo 39:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=9'>Lev 8:9</a> <br/> - Respect due to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=5'>Act 23:5</a> <br/> - Duties of:<br/> b Had charge of the sanctuary and altar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=2'>Num 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=5'>Num 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=7'>Num 18:7</a><br/> b to offer sacrifices<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=1'>Heb 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=8&verse=3'>Heb 8:3</a><br/> b to designate subordinate priests for duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=19'>Num 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=36'>1Sa 2:36</a><br/> b to officiate in consecrations of Levites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=21'>Num 8:21</a><br/> b to have charge of the treasury<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=12&verse=10'>2Ki 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=4'>2Ki 22:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=14'>2Ch 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=9'>2Ch 34:9</a><br/> b to light the lamps of tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=8'>Exo 30:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=4'>Lev 24:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=3'>Num 8:3</a><br/> b to burn incense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=8'>Exo 30:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=28'>1Sa 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=13'>1Ch 23:13</a><br/> b to place shewbread on the table every Sabbath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=8'>Lev 24:8</a><br/> b to offer for his own sins of ignorance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=12'>Lev 4:12</a><br/> b on the Day of Atonement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=10'>Exo 30:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16'>Lev 16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=3'>Heb 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=7'>Heb 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=23'>Heb 9:23</a><br/> b Judicial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=15'>Num 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=13'>Deu 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Sa 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=4'>Hos 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=3'>Mat 26:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=50'>Mat 26:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=57'>Mat 26:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=62'>Mat 26:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=28'>Act 5:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=5'>Act 23:5</a><br/> b to number the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=3'>Num 1:3</a><br/> b Officiate at choice of ruler<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=19'>Num 27:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=21'>Num 27:21</a><br/> b Distribute spoils of war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=29'>Num 31:29</a><br/> - Emoluments (compensations) of:<br/> <a href='S:Priest, Emoluments (Compensations) of'>Priest, Emoluments (Compensations) of</a> <br/> - A second priest, under the high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=32'>Num 3:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=16'>Num 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=6'>Num 31:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=20'>1Ch 9:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=24'>2Sa 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=18'>2Ki 25:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=2'>Luk 3:2</a> <br/> Miscellaneous facts concerning:<br/> - Loyal to Rehoboam at the time of the revolt of the ten tribes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=13'>2Ch 11:13</a> <br/> - Zeal of, in purging the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=17'>2Ch 29:17</a> <br/> - Wickedness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=14'>2Ch 36:14</a> <br/> - Taken with the captivity to Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=1'>Jer 29:1</a> <br/> - Return from the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=1&verse=5'>Ezr 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=39'>Ezr 2:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=61'>Ezr 2:61</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=70'>Ezr 2:70</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=8'>Ezr 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=7'>Ezr 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=30'>Ezr 8:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=42'>Neh 7:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=73'>Neh 7:73</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=8'>Neh 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=7'>Neh 12:7</a> <br/> - Polluted by marrying idolatrous wives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=2'>Ezr 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=5'>Ezr 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=19'>Ezr 10:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=28'>Neh 10:28</a> <br/> - Restore the altar, and offer sacrifices<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=7'>Ezr 3:7</a> <br/> - Supervise the building of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=13'>Ezr 3:13</a> <br/> - Inquire of John the Baptist whether he were the Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles